 block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip: <\/strong>There are <strong>15 hot springs<\/strong> in Karlovy Vary, all situated within or next to beautiful buildings. Most of the big springs look like fountains, whereas the small stone bowls are the drinkable ones.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/42913&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111720\/things-to-do-karlovy-vary-czech-republic-1.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111720\/things-to-do-karlovy-vary-czech-republic-1-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111720\/things-to-do-karlovy-vary-czech-republic-1-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"10 Things to do in Karlovy Vary, Czech Republic\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>2. St Mary Magdalene Church<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>St Mary Magdalene is not your regular church. It&#x2019;s a breathtaking baroque church, with a beautiful white facade, clock faces, and two striking green-domed towers. It&#x2019;s iconic to Karlovy Vary, overlooking the city at all times, and located close to the main hot spring.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111758\/karlovy-vary-St-Mary-Magdalene-Church-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"karlovy vary St Mary Magdalene Church\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"karlovy vary St Mary Magdalene Church\" class=\"wp-image-43091 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111758\/karlovy-vary-St-Mary-Magdalene-Church-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111758\/karlovy-vary-St-Mary-Magdalene-Church-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111758\/karlovy-vary-St-Mary-Magdalene-Church-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111758\/karlovy-vary-St-Mary-Magdalene-Church-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111758\/karlovy-vary-St-Mary-Magdalene-Church-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/stati