ld\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111801\/Grand-Hotel-Pupp-Karlovy-Vary.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>The fascinating history of the hotel has made it the setting for famous movies. For example, the James Bond film &#x2018;Casino Royale&#x2019;, and &#x2018;The Last Holiday&#x2019;. Not only that, but it&#x2019;s thought to be the inspiration behind Wes Anderson&#x2019;s &#x2018;&#x2018;The Grand Budapest Hotel&#x2019;. Visit the hotel&#x2019;s cafe for a drink, and take the opportunity to breathe in the luxury, and cinematic prestige; an absolute top thing to do in Karlovy Vary!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/grand-hotel-pupp\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your stay at Grand Hotel Pupp<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111754\/Grand-Hotel-Pupp-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"Grand Hotel Pupp\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Grand Hotel P