iner\">\n<p>Because guests were visiting from all over the world, different religious places of worship were also built in the area. For example, the breathtaking Orthodox Church of Peter and Paul.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111832\/Things-to-do-Karlovy-Vary-Church-St-Peter-and-Paul.jpg\" alt=\"Things to do Karlovy Vary Church St Peter and Paul\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"323\" alt=\"Things to do Karlovy Vary Church St Peter and Paul\" class=\"wp-image-43066 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111832\/Things-to-do-Karlovy-Vary-Church-St-Peter-and-Paul.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111832\/Things-to-do-Karlovy-Vary-Church-St-Peter-and-Paul-300x215.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111832\/Things-to-do-Karlovy-Vary-Church-St-Peter-and-Paul-600x431.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111832\/Things-to-do-Karlovy-Vary-Church-St-Peter-and-Paul-800x575.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111832\/Things-to-do-Karlovy-Vary-Church-St-Peter-and-Paul-1080x776.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111832\/Things-to-do-Karlovy-Vary-Church-St-Peter-and-Paul-450x323.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111832\/Things-to-do-Karlovy-Vary-Church-St-Peter-and-Paul-1536x1103.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111832\/Things-to-do-Karlovy-Vary-Church-St-Peter-and-Paul-30x22.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111832\/Things-to-do-Karlovy-Vary-