               <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">How to get there:<\/strong> Choose from a 3.5 or 1.5 km hike to reach the top. Note that the 1.5 km hike starts from the stop of bus number 8 in Hurky.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111829\/Things-to-do-Karlovy-Vary-Goethes-Lookout-Tower.jpg\" alt=\"Things to do Karlovy Vary Goethes Lookout Tower\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"323\" alt=\"Things to do Karlovy Vary Goethes Lookout Tower\" class=\"wp-image-43067 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111829\/Things-to-do-Karlovy-Vary-Goethes-Lookout-Tower.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111829\/Things-to-do-Karlovy-Vary-Goethes-Lookout-Tower-300x215.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111829\/Things-to-do-Karlovy-Vary-Goethes-Lookout-Tower-600x431.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111829\/Things-to-do-Karlovy-Vary-Goethes-Lookout-Tower-800x575.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111829\/Things-to-do-Karlovy-Vary-Goethes-Lookout-Tower-1080x776.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111829\/Things-to-do-Karlovy-Vary-Goethes-Lookout-Tower-450x323.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111829\/Things-to-do-Karlovy-Vary-Goethes-Lookout-Tower-1536x1103.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111829\/Things-to-do-Karlovy-Vary-Goethes-Lookout-Tower-30x22.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111829\/Things-to-do-Karlovy-Vary-Goethes-Lookout-Tower-163x117.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111829\/Things-to-do-Karlovy-Vary-Goethes-Lookout-Tower-251x180.jpg 251w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111829\/Things-to-do-Karlovy-Vary-Goethes-Lookout-Tower-768x552.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111829\/Things-to-do-Karlovy-Vary-Goethes-Lookout-Tower-1024x735.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111829\/Things-to-do-Karlovy-Vary-Goethes-Lookout-Tower-1440x1034.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111829\/Things-to-do-Karlovy-Vary-Goethes-Lookout-Tower-30x22.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/23111829\/Things-to-do-Karlovy-Vary-Goethes-Lookout-Tower.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>10. Loket&#xA0;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have time, visit the picturesque town Loket, located 14km from Karlovy Vary. People mostly visit for the 13th century Loket castle, which sits above the town. The word &#x2018;Loket&#x2019; means &#x2018;elbow&#x2019; in Czech, as the fairytale castle was built in the elbow of the river. Because of Loket&#x2019;s location on a bend of the Oh&#x159;e river, it has the unique outlook of the river on 3 sides of the town. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">How to get there:<\/strong> Take bus number 6 from Karlovy Vary. It&#x2019;s also possible to travel by train in 25 minutes but most trains are not direct.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"hotels\">Where to Stay in Karlovy Vary<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>There are numerous hotels with spas to pick from in Karlovy Vary. Pick one of our favorites below or <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hotels-karlovy-vary\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">see all hotels<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"products__container\">\n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/dvorak-karlovy\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Dvorak\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23112843\/Dvorak-450x245.jpg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">Dvorak<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/